	</div>

</section>

<ul class="modules large-block-grid-3 small-block-grid-1 show-for-medium-up">
	<li class="about-us">
		<h1>About Us</h1>
		<p>Learn about us and how we came to be.</p>
		<a href="about" class="button">Learn more</a>
